{{Quote|Now then&hellip; what's that I smell? Could it be some of those famous Wookiee-ookiees?|[[Saun Dann]]|<ref name="The Star Wars Holiday Special">''[[The Star Wars Holiday Special]]''</ref>}}
'''Wookiee-ookiees''' were a type of [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] [[Foodstuff/Legends|food]]. [[Lumpawaroo/Legends|Lumpawaroo]] was fond of these treats, as when he was young, his mother [[Mallatobuck/Legends|Mallatobuck]] commonly made them for him. [[Saun Dann]] also enjoyed Malla's Wookiee-ookiees.

Media mogul [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] also shared the recipe on his [[Baobab HoloNet]].

